    <abstract id="aspace_533ab4241ebcce08afd3fe0cfdb050c7">This collection documents the efforts of the grass-roots organization known as The Drive to Protect the Ladies' Mile to designate this area in Manhattan as a historic district. It includes letters of support, research, submissions to the Landmarks Commission, and related materials.</abstract>
